# UI styling

`lang`/`dir` on **root layout only** (`src/lib/app-locale.ts`). **Logical Tailwind** (`me`/`ms`, `start`/`end`, …).

**shadcn** from `src/components/ui` — default variants; **never hand-edit `src/components/ui/*`**. App behavior in `src/app/**` or `src/components/` (outside `ui/`); regen primitives via shadcn CLI.

Reuse UI up the tree; hoist to highest relevant scope — [architecture.md § Placement](docs/agents/architecture.md#placement).

**Detail (Read):** [docs/agents/ui-design.md](docs/agents/ui-design.md).
